Apple has stated it will sell its HomePod smart speaker in Canada, France, and Germany from 18 June 2018. The HomePod is currently available in the US, UK, and Australia, and sells for $349 – available in white and space grey. Apple also announced that iOS 11.4 supports HomePod stereo pairs and a new multi-room audio system. “This free software update introduces the most advanced, easy to use, wireless multi-room audio system using AirPlay 2 to play music in any room from any room,” said Apple. The HomePod is compatible with the iPhone 5s or later and various iPad models, with iOS 11.2.5 or later.